{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before even we started work-- and this was for the first time in my life that I have seen-- they put us-- you know, we were very dirty, traveling that many weeks without a wash.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had lice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was dirty, so they put us into Russian barnyard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what it-- what-- how'd you say it in English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's like a big bath house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know But few hundred women undressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I was twelve, and it's for-- for the first time, this wasn't a society like now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've never seen a naked woman, and for the first time in my life, I suddenly saw a few hundred women, old and young, everybody naked.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took away your clothes, and they put it-- it was called delousing, you know, and they sterilize it or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to have a good wash, scrub, and later on, they got us back the clothes, and we were given little huts also. 10 people into one room.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how did we survive?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my father was-- well, my father was put to work in a forest, cutting trees, and the trees would go with the river.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would send them with the river to the nearest whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what they were using them for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But look, my father was a person that-- from a city, and I don't think he's ever seen in his life that many trees or all that, but he had to do it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was bitterly cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was given a job in the kitchen at the beginning to peel potatoes, which didn't last long because you had to bring your own knife.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
